      "date": "2015-06-01 22:40:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi Alex,\n\nFrom the log file, https://jira.hpdd.intel.com/secure/attachment/18032/lustre-log.1432924195.104212.txt.gz, the migration process failed at a non-existing file, then in the cleaning up path of mdd_object_create(), it tried to destroy the objects it has created and then hit this assertion.\n\nThe non-existing file part needs further investigation but the false assertion looks pretty straightforward to me.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
